{"tid":2189831,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警涉助管理賭場押後審","createTime":"2020-09-05T07:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T07:23:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"500710a20a98d744c3a3bac737c673ca9117c952","tid":2189831,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:16:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200905/K7N6POTRW5EKFP44TD3VTKVH3I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200905%2FK7N6POTRW5EKFP44TD3VTKVH3I%2F&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs406%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=471ae906\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200905%2FK7N6POTRW5EKFP44TD3VTKVH3I%2F&h=ef573ae7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200905/K7N6POTRW5EKFP44TD3VTKVH3I/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警涉助管理賭場押後審<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/X7KvUo7i6afY4hIm7vYgFDRVhFA=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NELG6UPDOJCCTO6NYLNPEAKVTA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FX7KvUo7i6afY4hIm7vYgFDRVhFA%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNELG6UPDOJCCTO6NYLNPEAKVTA.jpg&h=c6d10b2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■52歲高級警員潘藝志被控協助管理賭場。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方今年5月揭發屯門工廈一單位有非法賭檔，拘捕10男女，包括兩名警員，起訴其中一人協助管理賭場，案件昨提堂。男警聲稱需時從英國聘請大狀來港打官司，要求押後答辯，裁判官質疑「你都唔知佢幾時到你又要求延期」，最後只准延至本月30日聽取答辯。<br />\n<br />\n涉案共10名被告，八人為賭客，另兩人為報稱商人的陳偉麒（47歲），被。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱要從英國聘大狀<br />\n<br />\n兩人申請暫時毋須答辯，潘稱需時從英國聘請大律師蘇啟昌代表他，對方到港後需接受隔離，故申請押後案件。署理主任裁判官張潔宜問律師何時到港，潘直言「唔清楚」。張官謂「我已經畀咗兩星期有多你，英國返嚟乜都夠」；又問「其他事務律師係咪全部飛晒去英國呀」，最終拒絕押後更長時間，下令案件再提堂時答辯。<br />\n<br />\n餘下八名賭客年齡18至。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：TMCC1565/20"},{"pid":"a0b03edb5ac388e07159576235840242a8018410","tid":2189831,"uid":156511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:18:08.000Z","msg":"大波嬅: 唔告喇，case close"},{"pid":"2b9a77e5985b39e6d18fb79a063714b077366240","tid":2189831,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0b03edb5ac388e07159576235840242a8018410","tid":2189831,"uid":156511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:18:08.000Z","msg":"大波嬅: 唔告喇，case close"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:21:41.000Z","msg":"驊驊：無律師！證明無得夾口供<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即係無罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e5a0d7b74b0a4d2e91aba83651364573367544","tid":2189831,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:22:33.000Z","msg":"放心啦 ! 轉個圈就會撤控, 你當老波驊 流架 家陣 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8933e311dd1ad324cd7f65900a2b4ac7ae0710df","tid":2189831,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:23:05.000Z","msg":"「其他事務律師係咪全部飛晒去英國呀」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}